OL,3,CReeves drawing up plans to help with
OL,4,Cenergy costs as Iran war continues
OL,6,FTargeted support could be offered to
OL,7,Fhouseholds struggling with soaring
OL,8,Fenergy bills as a result of the Middle
OL,9,FEast crisis, Rachel Reeves has
OL,10,Findicated.
OL,12,FThe Chancellor said she would give
OL,13,Fsupport "to those who really need it",
OL,14,Fwith a package of help for people who
OL,15,Frely on heating oil, which is not
OL,16,Fcovered by the energy price cap,
OL,17,Fexpected next week.
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@eO]
