OL,3,CReeves drawing up plans to help with
OL,4,Cenergy costs as Iran war continues
OL,6,FIn an interview with The Times, Ms
OL,7,FReeves indicated a subsidy package
OL,8,Fwould be set out next week: "I have
OL,9,Ffound the money and we've worked
OL,10,Fthrough with MPs and others a response
OL,11,Ffor people who are not protected by
OL,12,Fthe energy price cap.
OL,14,F"We're giving greater support to those
OL,15,Fwho really need it."
OL,17,FThere is more time to draw up a plan
OL,18,Ffor gas and electricity bills, because
OL,19,Fof the price cap.
OL,26,@pD@]OUvD@AOUwD@TO]
