OL,3,CReeves drawing up plans to help with
OL,4,Cenergy costs as Iran war continues
OL,6,FAnalysts at Cornwall Insight have
OL,7,Fforecast that household energy bills
OL,8,Fcould rise by 10% from July following
OL,9,Fsharp increases in wholesale gas
OL,10,Fprices.
OL,12,FThis would mean Ofgem's price cap for
OL,13,FJuly to September surges to #1,801 a
OL,14,Fyear for a typical dual fuel household
OL,15,F` an increase of #160 or 10% on
OL,16,FApril's cap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
