PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773637426
OL,3,CReeves drawing up plans to help with
OL,4,Cenergy costs as Iran war continues
OL,6,F"We've got some time, and we are
OL,7,Fworking through in the Iran response
OL,8,Fboard (a group of Treasury ministers
OL,9,Fand officials) different approaches
OL,10,Fthat we could take, including looking
OL,11,Fat more targeted options," the
OL,12,FChancellor told The Times.
OL,14,F"We are working through different
OL,15,Fscenarios at the moment and I don't
OL,16,Fwant to suggest that we're going to do
OL,17,Fsomething that we know we're not able
OL,18,Fto deliver.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773637426
OL,3,CReeves drawing up plans to help with
OL,4,Cenergy costs as Iran war continues
OL,6,F"I am concerned given how high our
OL,7,Fdebt is, the debt that we inherited,
OL,8,Fand so I want to look at what the
OL,9,Fdifferent options available would be."
OL,11,FShe played down the prospect of a
OL,12,Fblanket energy bailout for households,
OL,13,Fas happened in the wake of Russia's
OL,14,Finvasion of Ukraine at the cost of
OL,15,Fabout #35 billion over a six-month
OL,16,Fperiod.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
